        "primary": {
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "heading2",
              "text": "Designing the Future of Emirati Perfumery",
              "spans": []
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "The Anfasic flagship at Dubai Mall reimagines traditional perfume retail into a futuristic, immersive environment. Curved forms, glowing violet tones, and reflective surfaces create a space that feels both rooted in Emirati culture and ahead of its time. This store became the first physical expression of Anfasic’s rebranding, a bold step into modern luxury design within one of the world’s most prestigious retail destinations.",
              "spans": []
            }
          ]
        },
